75
00:09:09.497 --> 00:09:11.997
- Couldn't stop him.
- Neither could I.

76
00:09:15.457 --> 00:09:16.722
I lost the kid.

77
00:09:19.457 --> 00:09:21.392
Tony. we lost.

78
00:09:23.574 --> 00:09:25.136
Is. umm...

79
