Which of course he did. but there's a
lot of that goin' around. ain't there?

94
00:10:31.162 --> 00:10:34.369
Honestly. at this exact second. I
thought you were a Build-A-Bear.

95
00:10:34.394 --> 00:10:35.357
Maybe I am.

96
00:10:35.382 --> 00:10:37.319
We've been hunting Thanos
for three weeks now.

97
00:10:37.450 --> 00:10:41.043
Deep space scans. and
satellites. and we got nothing.

98
00:10:43.218 --> 00:10:45.686
- Tony you fought him.
- Who told you that?

99
00:10:45.826 --> 00:10:46.826
Didn't fight him.

100
00:10:46.904 --> 00:10:49.145
No. He wiped my face
with a planet while a

101
00:10:49.170 --> 00:10:51.514
Bleecker Street magician
gave away the stone.

102
00:10:51.592 --> 00:10:53.381
- That's what happened. There was no fight...
- Okay.

103
00:10:53.405 --> 00:10:54.155


104
00:10:54.180 --> 00:10:56.867
Did he give you any clues?
Any coordinates. anything?

105
00:10:57.805 --> 00:10:58.805
Pfft!

106
