- And I needed you.

109
00:11:08.265 --> 00:11:12.381
As in past tense. That trumps what
you need. It's too late. buddy.

110
00:11:12.749 --> 00:11:13.749
Sorry.

111
00:11:14.866 --> 00:11:17.467
You know what I need?
I need to shave.

112
00:11:18.273 --> 00:11:21.764
- And I believe I rememeber telling
- Tony. Tony. Tony...

113
00:11:21.827 --> 00:11:23.711
why that otherwise.

114
00:11:23.736 --> 00:11:28.190
that what we needed was a suit of armor
around the world. Remember that?

115
00:11:28.215 --> 00:11:32.660
Whether it impacted our precious
freedoms. or not. That's what we needed.

116
00:11:32.685 --> 00:11:35.224
