- I said we'd lose.

117
00:11:35.337 --> 00:11:38.212
You said. "We'll do
that together. too."

118
00:11:38.268 --> 00:11:40.899
Well guess what. Cap? We lost.

119
00:11:40.938 --> 00:11:43.338
