Not the Prevengers?

122
00:11:50.040 --> 00:11:52.736
Okay. You made your point.
Just sit down. okay?

123
00:11:52.838 --> 00:11:55.408
- No. no. Here's my... She's great. by the way.
- Tony. sit. sit down!

124
00:11:55.456 --> 00:11:57.862
We need you. You're new blood.
Bunch of tired old mills...

125
00:11:57.900 --> 00:12:01.380
I got nothing for you. Cap.
I got no coordinates.

126
00:12:01.405 --> 00:12:04.314
no clues. no strategies.
no options...

127
00:12:04.339 --> 00:12:08.295
Zero. Zip. Nada. No
trust. you liar...

128
00:12:12.655 --> 00:12:15.662
Here. take this. You find
him and you put that on.

129
00:12:16.539 --> 00:12:17.804
You hide.

130
00:12:19.369 --> 00:12:22.344
- Tony!
- I'm fine. I...

131
00:12:29.674 --> 00:12:33.455
Bruce gave him a sedative. He's gonna
probably be out for the rest of the day.

132
00:12:33.783 --> 00:12:37.174
You guys take care of him. And I'll bring
an Bezurian elixir when I come back.

133
00:12:37.822 --> 00:12:40.298
- Where are you going?
- To kill Thanos.

134
