142
00:13:05.561 --> 00:13:09.326
Then when he worked. he
talked about his great plan.

143
00:13:09.709 --> 00:13:12.303
Even disassembled. I
wanted to please him.

144
00:13:12.858 --> 00:13:17.053
I'd ask. where would we go
once his plan was complete?

145
00:13:18.170 --> 00:13:20.237
His answer was always the same.

146
00:13:24.406 --> 00:13:25.531
To The Garden.

147
00:13:25.789 --> 00:13:28.820
That's cute. Thanos has
a retirement plan.

148
00:13:28.845 --> 00:13:30.493
So where is he. then?

149
00:13:30.556 --> 00:13:32.304
When Thanos snapped his fingers.

150
00:13:32.329 --> 00:13:36.860
Earth became ground zero for a power surge
of ridiculously cosmic proportions.

151
00:13:36.907 --> 00:13:41.188
No one's ever seen anything like it...
until two days ago.

152
00:13:42.321 --> 00:13:44.617
On this planet.

153
00:13:44.946 --> 00:13:46.289
