- Look. he still got the stones. so...
- So let's get him.

158
00:13:57.012 --> 00:13:59.706
- We use them to bring everyone back.
- Just like that?

159
00:13:59.868 --> 00:14:01.696
Yeah. Just like that.

160
00:14:01.721 --> 00:14:04.876
