244
00:26:39.656 --> 00:26:42.381
- Well. you were closer.
- Yeah. And now we smell like garbage.

245
00:26:42.406 --> 00:26:44.278
You get a reading
on those tremors?

246
00:26:44.303 --> 00:26:46.795
It was a mild subduction
under the African plate.

247
00:26:46.914 --> 00:26:49.328
Do we have a visual? How
are we handling it?

248
00:26:49.359 --> 00:26:52.593
Nat. it's an earthquake
under the ocean.

249
00:26:52.625 --> 00:26:55.592
